    "en": {
      "title": "Government employees will work normally from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A circular has been issued informing public sector employees to report to work as usual from tomorrow (24th). The Treasury Secretary has issued the circular informing all the heads of government agencies.",
        "Due to the existing fuel problem, the calling of civil servants to work was limited."
